      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Henry W. Fairweather, one Of\nthe Oldest former Northern Pacific\nofficials In this section of the coun-\ntry, is writing the history Of the\nNorthern Pacific railroad from the\ntime the road was proposed until it\nwent into the hands of the receiver.\nThe history is being written by a\nman who was with the road from\nthe beginning to the end of that\nperiod. He was superintendent for\nmany years and then came to Spo,\nkane where he engaged in the bank\ning business.\n\n\nThe history will be printed In an\neastern magazine and then put in\nbook form."
